  "detailed_description": "<h1>欢迎加入官方QQ群一起讨论游戏</h1><p>江华号官方QQ群：783142360</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2513140/extras/c5c030f267728d69358550fb696c2557.avif?t=1707274266\" width=600 height=343 /></span><br>民国17年，汉口延庆里杨宅举办了一场葬礼，头七夜间竟发生了诡异的还魂事件。《楚城时报》新人记者虞慧龄孤身一人前往采访，却被种种谜团指引着登上了豪华客轮“江华号”。<br>调查现场、破解谜题、收集线索、推理真相。重重迷雾之下，一场精彩纷呈、交织时代与信念的冒险之旅就此展开！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2513140/extras/29941a8bbfe4696acee9aa53b2a6f116.poster.avif?t=1707274266\" width=600 height=71 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2513140/extras/29941a8bbfe4696acee9aa53b2a6f116.webm?t=1707274266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2513140/extras/6b7a1050e478e0a300ff2814b8581e19.avif?t=1707274266\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>《江华号》是一款横版剧情向解谜游戏。玩家将通过调查场景中的线索、破解各种谜题、与充满时代感的各位Npc交谈等方式，逐步推理出案件真相，并由此发掘隐藏在案件背后不为人知的隐秘往事。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2513140/extras/0ac9e9267984d940ef16347babab6561.avif?t=1707274266\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>扑朔迷离、耐人寻味的故事</strong>——民国年代，风云激荡。以新人记者虞慧龄为视角，带你揭开隐藏在江华号辉煌外表之下的隐秘过往。商场的尔虞我诈，世事的冷酷无常，难以磨灭的执念……一切都将化入时代的滚滚洪流之中。<br><br></li><li><strong>妙趣横生的谜题玩法</strong>——每个谜题都经过精心设计，难度适中，绝不会触碰你的耐心底线。<br><br></li><li><strong>民国风情，武汉特色</strong>——民国时期的武汉是中国第二大经济中心，有着“东方芝加哥”的美誉。游戏内包含大量写实可考的民国武汉细节，小到一张海报、一首童谣、一碗藕汤、一段码头号子，都尽可能呈现出原汁原味的老武汉风情。<br><br></li><li><strong>定格时光的收集系统</strong>——发挥虞慧龄的新闻记者特长，去收集那些具有民国色彩的事物吧！也许是一样物品、一个文化符号，让这些收集品将悠悠时光定格在这一瞬间。<br><br></li><li><strong>精致耐看的美术风格</strong>——国风水墨笔触与西洋建筑场景相结合，完美体现民国东西方文化交融的气质。<br><br></li><li><strong>丰富有趣的成就系统</strong>——游戏内有大量的成就以供获得，这些成就也许严肃认真、也许稀奇古怪、也许幽默搞笑，有空的话就收集看看吧！</li></ul><br><strong>精致美术，武汉特色</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2513140/extras/454a55ffc2584e85c1d2a2e614b0b190.poster.avif?t=1707274266\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2513140/extras/454a55ffc2584e85c1d2a2e614b0b190.webm?t=1707274266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2513140/extras/454a55ffc2584e85c1d2a2e614b0b190.mp4?t=1707274266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>趣味互动，暗藏线索</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2513140/extras/340b2d00134d61557700a76f4301188a.poster.avif?t=1707274266\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2513140/extras/340b2d00134d61557700a76f4301188a.webm?t=1707274266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2513140/extras/340b2d00134d61557700a76f4301188a.mp4?t=1707274266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>怀旧元素，民国风情</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2513140/extras/176007340d7699cf329b9684bb1092b6.poster.avif?t=1707274266\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2513140/extras/176007340d7699cf329b9684bb1092b6.webm?t=1707274266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2513140/extras/176007340d7699cf329b9684bb1092b6.mp4?t=1707274266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
