ong>——游戏内有大量的成就以供获得，这些成就也许严肃认真、也许稀奇古怪、也许幽默搞笑，有空的话就收集看看吧！</li></ul><br><strong>精致美术，武汉特色</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2513140/extras/454a55ffc2584e85c1d2a2e614b0b190.poster.avif?t=1707274266\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2513140/extras/454a55ffc2584e85c1d2a2e614b0b190.webm?t=1707274266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2513140/extras/454a55ffc2584e85c1d2a2e614b0b190.mp4?t=1707274266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>趣味互动，暗藏线索</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2513140/extras/340b2d00134d61557700a76f4301188a.poster.avif?t=1707274266\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2513140/extras/340b2d00134d61557700a76f4301188a.webm?t=1707274266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2513140/extras/340b2d00134d61557700a76f4301188a.mp4?t=1707274266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>怀旧元素，民国风情</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2513140/extras/176007340d7699cf329b9684bb1092b6.poster.avif?t=1707274266\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2513140/extras/176007340d7699cf329b9684bb1092b6.webm?t=1707274266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2513140/extras/176007340d7699cf329b9684bb1092b6.mp4?t=170727